    "name": "SLEEP HERD",
    "steam_appid": 3045180,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>《牧梦记》：深入黑暗梦幻仙境，开启2-4人协作生存之旅！</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045180/extras/d6e71558b67702fdd41f455c63d920f9.avif?t=1766268541\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045180/extras_big/d6e71558b67702fdd41f455c63d920f9.avif?t=1766268541 width=800 height=255 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>隐藏在柔和牧场与荆棘树林之外的便是“梦境”：一座由模糊记忆编织而成、弥漫着神秘熟悉感的迷宫。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索、收集、战斗、照亮前路！在这款2-4人合作资源管理游戏中，踏入一个黑暗而梦幻的奇境！穿越柔和牧场与荆棘树林，揭开笼罩在神秘熟悉感中的“梦境”之谜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045180/extras/b7c92348c0e9b95e1161517dd806e8b5.avif?t=1766268541\" alt=\"抓住\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045180/extras_big/b7c92348c0e9b95e1161517dd806e8b5.webp?t=1766268541 width=1600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045180/extras/d8f1fdeb97fb69454a6a47edc593c499.avif?t=1766268541\" alt=\"扔出\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045180/extras_big/d8f1fdeb97fb69454a6a47edc593c499.webp?t=1766268541 width=1600 height=292 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045180/extras/0649ea9a6fbba2ee5dcc3e110d8044ef.avif?t=1766268541\" alt=\"巡游\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045180/extras_big/0649ea9a6fbba2ee5dcc3e110d8044ef.webp?t=1766268541 width=1600 height=351 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演四位独特的手工娃娃：任性的<strong>嘟嘟（Beep）</strong>、瞌睡的<strong>考夫（Kovsky）</strong>、尽责的<strong>查伊（Tchai）</strong>、时髦的<strong>小啵（Bo）</strong>。引导一群好奇的羊灵，它们渴望帮助你探索隐藏秘密、穿越重重障碍，并应对潜伏于阴影中的不速之客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045180/extras/f7c2617aff6b739738844d34a5fc2ecc.poster.avif?t=1766268541\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045180/extras/f7c2617aff6b739738844d34a5fc2ecc.webm?t=1766268541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045180/extras/f7c2617aff6b739738844d34a5fc2ecc.mp4?t=1766268541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索梦境奇境</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跨越蜿蜒庄园与缤纷糕点世界（第一幕前两章），总计三幕六章的完整战役！运用你的指引之光驯服游荡的野羊，指挥这支灵魂仪仗队搬运物品、破除障碍、解开合作谜题，并抵御捕食者。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集珍贵之物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >梦境中散落着维系壁炉之火的补给、强化玩法的物品，以及承载失落记忆的纪念品。在壁炉旁收集纪念品，壮大你的羊群，逐步拼凑出梦境背后的真相。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >智慧管理求生</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的光芒会流逝，壁炉之火也将摇曳！在组织羊群时务必留意它们的光芒。与队友协作：分头行动扩大探索范围，或紧密合作深入险境。在夜幕降临时与时间赛跑，直面黑暗！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合作创造回忆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握地图，挖掘阴影中的故事碎片！与团队紧密配合，共同提升你们的“纪念分”，在逆境中留下深刻的合作印记。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045180/extras/a2c6a15e192f7b0f85b2375ace166fd2.avif?t=1766268541\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045180/extras_big/a2c6a15e192f7b0f85b2375ace166fd2.avif?t=1766268541 width=800 height=163 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为梦境的守护牧羊人！</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-4人在线合作生存冒险</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四位性格鲜明的可玩娃娃（嘟嘟、考夫、查伊、小啵）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三幕六章的完整奇幻战役旅程</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验梦境中展开的动人故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >达成成就，解锁精彩内容！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重要通知</strong>：《牧梦记》暂未支持简体中文。愿望单数量将直接决定语言支持优先级！渴望体验中文版？立刻点击[加入愿望单]！你的支持是中文版实现的关键！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
